videos.description: Moritz Wagner scores a game-high 16 points in Michigan's 62-47 win against Rutgers.

videos.description: Jude Stamper suffers from a condition that prevents him from bending his joints but that doesn't mean he can't become a valuable member of the Wolverines. On Sunday, fans and coaches wore bow-ties to honor the youngster.
